title: Gehou 1.1.1 - A Modern Restaurant & Cafe Theme
description: Visit us on: https://www.nulledforums.org If there are no seeds, use our forum for direct download links! Gehou WordPress Theme is responsive Modern Restaurant & Cafe WordPress Theme with clean,modern and elegant design.It can be used for restaurant or cafe to show services & foods. Its build based on twitter bootstrap ,so it has powerfull features. Gehou WordPress Theme Features [*]Fully Customizable. You can edit or create your own layout almost on every page/element. [*]Drag & drop Page Builder [*]Prebuilt Layout/Template [*]Custom Elements for Page Builder [*]Predefined Header & Footer and Custom Header & Custom Footer. Build your own header/footer using the page builder. [*]Predefined blog templates, and Blog Custom Layout. Create your own style for blog page using the page builder. [*]Inline Editor. You can change directly the content inside most of the custom element of page builder. [*]Different Post Style/Format. Video, Audio, Slider,Image, Galleries. Or you can create your own layout using the page builder. [*]Blog Post Wide(without sidebar) or using Sidebar [*]One Click Demo Importer. Import everything on demo page with only single click and you’re done!
